OL,3,CMum says anti-choking device 'saved
OL,4,Cson's life'
OL,6,FA family whose toddler started choking
OL,7,Fon a cocktail sausage say an at-home
OL,8,Fdevice "saved his life".
OL,10,FWhen Charlie Campbell-Hills' son
OL,11,FEdward, aged 2, got into difficulties,
OL,12,Fshe first tried the conventional
OL,13,Fmethod of slapping him on the back,
OL,14,Fbut without success.
OL,16,FThe family from the New Forest in
OL,17,FHampshire had recently acquired an
OL,18,Fanti-choking kit, which managed to
OL,19,Fsuck out the blockage on the second
OL,20,Fattempt.
