OL,3,CMum says anti-choking device 'saved
OL,4,Cson's life'
OL,6,FResuscitation Council UK, however,
OL,7,Fsays it does not support the use of
OL,8,Fanti-choking devices as there is not
OL,9,Fenough research and evidence for their
OL,10,Fsafety.
OL,12,FEdward's mum, Charlie Campbell-Hills
OL,13,Fsaid: "It was tea time before bath and
OL,14,Fbed, he didn't quite chew properly
OL,15,Flike a toddler sometimes does, he
OL,16,Fswallowed down a big chunk of sausage
OL,17,Fand stopped breathing.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
