OL,3,CMum says anti-choking device 'saved
OL,4,Cson's life'
OL,6,F"I immediately started backslaps, but
OL,7,Fit made no difference. I scooped him
OL,8,Fup, ran into the kitchen, grabbed the
OL,9,FLifeVac, sat down on the floor with
OL,10,Fhim and was able to dislodge it at the
OL,11,Fsecond attempt.
OL,13,F"It hit me afterwards, it was
OL,14,Fobviously very scary at the time, but
OL,15,Fyou haven't got time to freak out or
OL,16,Fpanic. After he was ok, I then
OL,17,Frealised quite how terrifying that was.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
