OL,3,CMum says anti-choking device 'saved
OL,4,Cson's life'
OL,6,F"He gave me a cuddle and then asked
OL,7,Ffor some milk. It was me that was left
OL,8,Fa gibbering wreck afterwards, not
OL,9,FEdward."
OL,11,FEdward's Dad, Tom Campbell-Hills said:
OL,12,F"You don't want to think what could
OL,13,Fhave happened.
OL,15,F"We're incredibly lucky that only a
OL,16,Fweek before, after having introduced
OL,17,Fthe choking device at work, I brought
OL,18,Fone back home."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
