OL,3,CMum says anti-choking device 'saved
OL,4,Cson's life'
OL,6,FThe current advice to help a child who
OL,7,Fis choking is to give five sharp blows
OL,8,Fto the back, followed by five
OL,9,Fabdominal thrusts if the slaps do not
OL,10,Fwork, and then to call 999 for help if
OL,11,Fthey are still choking.
OL,13,FResuscitation Council UK said in a
OL,14,Fstatement: "We do not support their
OL,15,Fuse as there is insufficient research
OL,16,Fand evidence on the safety or
OL,17,Feffectiveness of these devices.
OL,19,F"We are concerned that these devices
OL,20,Fcould delay established treatments for
OL,21,Fchoking."
